body: "Findings:\n1. SECURITY: Scrubbed 192.168.x.x from 16 git-tracked pm item/history files\n2. TESTS: 81 files, 1087 tests pass; 67/67 dogfood commands verified\n3. SEARCH: Semantic/keyword/hybrid all working; 643 indexed items, 0 stale\n4. CODE QUALITY: command-aware.ts unused but valuable; undici+c8 unused deps; normalizeTimeoutMs duplicated in providers.ts and vector-stores.ts\n5. TELEMETRY: Stack healthy (API healthz OK, Grafana 302); analysis scripts in scripts/prod/telemetry/\n6. SENTRY: 8 issues all PmCliError (user input); scrubbing working; 20% trace rate appropriate\n7. CALENDAR: All views/formats/filters/recurrence working\n8. SDK: All 9 capability types exported; starter extension comprehensive\n9. OUTPUT: TOON 30-40% smaller than JSON; errors include structured next_steps/examples"
